==English==

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[juvenalis]]'', from ''[[juvenis]]'' "young one".

===Adjective===
'''juvenal'''
# Describes a young [[bird]] that has its first flying [[plumage]].

===Noun===
'''juvenal'''
# Such a bird.
# {{obsolete}} A [[juvenile]].

